Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:07.73,JP,,0000,0000,0000,,	第八話 Kindling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.01,0:24:10.20,JP,,0000,0000,0000,,	我らが大義に曇りなし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:14.65,CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	真噁心
